      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a handy fixer-upper? This vehicle is ready for someone with the right tools and a bit of know-how to get it back in top shape! It's being sold as-is, offering a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast to roll up their sleeves and bring out its potential. Perfect for those who love a rewarding weekend project!",
