    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is in great shape overall, though it does show minor signs of regular use such as small rock chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean and remains in excellent condition with minimal wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car is solid and reliable, having received regular oil changes and scheduled service, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
