    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rougher roads. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
