    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, representing a superior balance of performance and value. This unit features a robust mechanical profile and a well-preserved interior, ensuring a refined driving experience. Thoroughly vetted for operational integrity, it stands as a testament to consistent care and engineering excellence. We invite serious inquiries for this distinguished automotive investment.",
