      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride and it's looking for a great new home. It's in wonderful shape and has been super dependable for all my trips around town. It drives smoothly and has been well-cared for, so it's ready to hit the road with you today! It\u2019s a fantastic car that still has so much life left in it\u2014come see for yourself!",
