    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54B32 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features a fully serviced Double-VANOS system and recent valve clearance adjustments, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Drive is sent through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate floor fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension features refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers for precise turn-in and lateral stability. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and chassis integrity remain excellent for the enthusiast looking for a turn-key performance machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
