    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior features its original factory paint, which still holds a deep, impressive shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper\u2014honest wear that reflects its history as a dependable driver. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment and remains remarkably crisp; the seats are firm and free of any rips or staining, and the dashboard is free of cracks or sun damage. All power features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound, having undergone a recent professional multi-point inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and we have recently replaced the battery and performed a fresh synthetic oil change. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This car has been maintained with an open checkbook and is ready for its next chapter.",
